b'Bunbuku Chagama': b'A short film about a man who rescues a tanuki. When the tanuki transforms himself into a teapot, he is given to a temple as a gift. Once inside the temple, the tanuki reverts to his true form and causes havoc.\n\n(Source: AniDB)'
